n print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aAufklärung. 4aBarock. 4aGalante Literatur. 4aHunold, Christian Friedrich. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aBaroque.  aEnlightenment.  aGallant Literature.  aHunold, Christian Friedrich.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2012z9783110288896oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311026471540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311026477740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110264777423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110264777/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-GLCc2000d2014